data.description: A vibrant premier residential community in desirable Cross Creek.  Experience the elegance upon entering an innovative open floor concept, boasting with high ceiling and an abundance of natural light that brightens a perfect and relaxing interior design. A well-situated property surrounded by greeneries and a tranquil backyard oasis. Enjoy a Large size Master's bedroom with a spacious bath, walk-in closet, and double vanity sink. Cook your daily meal in a modern kitchen design with branded appliances, a huge walk-in pantry, and a laundry area.  This energy-efficient smart home is conveniently located for top-rated schools, offices, hospitals, hotels,  military installations, and shopping town centers. Turnkey ready to move in and enjoy amenities all-inclusive to homeowners and guests.
